1
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,760
Honey, where are you taking me?

2
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:08,599
Slow down, you're scaring me.

3
00:01:09,359 --> 00:01:10,040
Shut up!

4
00:01:10,319 --> 00:01:11,000
Shut up!

5
00:01:29,599 --> 00:01:30,239
Talk.

6
00:01:32,599 --> 00:01:33,959
How many men did you sleep with behind my back?

7
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,840
Honey, what are you saying?

8
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,680
I never did anything to wrong you.

9
00:01:43,239 --> 00:01:44,760
Didn't I warn you?

10
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:49,560
If I ever caught you cheating with another man,

11
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:51,400
I'd kill you.

12
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:54,879
I didn't! I don't know what you're talking about.

13
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:56,319
I swear I didn't.

14
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:58,120
I didn't.

15
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,560
Fine.

16
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,400
Not only do you sext online,

17
00:02:05,719 --> 00:02:06,920
seduce secretaries,

18
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,000
seduce photographers,

19
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,759
you think I don't know?

20
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,680
Hey, I'm a photographer too.

21
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:16,000
Why don't you have me take your photos?

22
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,879
The shoot was arranged by the company.

23
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,000
Liar.

24
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:22,000
Keep lying.

25
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,639
"Arranged by the company."

26
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:25,960
Let me tell you,

27
00:02:26,039 --> 00:02:27,159
you bitch.

28
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,960
Not only do you seduce men,

29
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:31,719
you're keeping a toy boy on the side, huh?

30
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:33,280
I really underestimated you.

31
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,039
What toy boy?

32
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:35,879
There isn't one.

33
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,560
Let me tell you,

34
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,560
monthly transfers.

35
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:42,120
The transfer records!

36
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:44,960
Keeping someone on the side.

37
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:46,439
No wonder lately

38
00:02:46,599 --> 00:02:48,400
you've been bringing less and less money home.

39
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:50,960
So you've been spending it on someone else, huh?

40
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:54,039
It's a misunderstanding!

41
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:55,120
A misunderstanding!

42
00:02:55,919 --> 00:02:57,919
Wiring money to someone is a misunderstanding?

43
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,759
Being lovey-dovey with him just now, also a misunderstanding?

44
00:02:59,759 --> 00:03:01,800
About to sleep together, that's a misunderstanding too?

45
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:03,560
Slut!

46
00:03:30,879 --> 00:03:31,639
Xiangxiang.

47
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,400
Xiangxiang.

48
00:03:34,439 --> 00:03:35,919
Xiangxiang, I was just kidding.

49
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:36,599
Xiangxiang.

50
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:37,960
Xiangxiang.

51
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,360
Xiangxiang!

52
00:03:45,319 --> 00:03:46,759
Don't you dare play dead on me!

53
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:49,319
Wake up! Wake up! Wake up!

54
00:03:59,599 --> 00:04:00,400
I killed someone.

55
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,840
I killed someone! I killed someone!

56
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,479
I killed someone!

57
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,240
I killed someone!

58
00:04:09,479 --> 00:04:10,280
I killed her!

59
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,920
Serves you right. You deserve to die.

60
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,160
You wronged me first.

61
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:32,639
You forced me to do this.

62
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:28,680
You dumped the body in Xinzhuang Ditch.

63
00:05:31,279 --> 00:05:32,519
Bullshit.

64
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:36,079
Liu Xiang's body was found in Liuye Lake.

65
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,560
I already admitted to the murder.

66
00:05:41,399 --> 00:05:42,920
Why would I lie now?

67
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:46,079
Did you hit Liu Xiang with your car before strangling her?

68
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:46,839
What?

69
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,879
Me, hit her with my car?

70
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:54,079
After I strangled her,

71
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,120
I pushed her into the ditch.

72
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,680
Then I drove off.

73
00:05:59,319 --> 00:06:01,079
Then why did you strip off her clothes?

74
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:04,240
And take the car to the shop to swap the front bumper?

75
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,040
I hit a dog.

76
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,959
Then who hit Liu Xiang?

77
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:15,560
I really did hit a dog.

78
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,120
Besides,

79
00:06:17,839 --> 00:06:18,439
besides,

80
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:21,120
why would I strip off her clothes?

81
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,560
Addicted to lying, are you?

82
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,240
Fang Ping.

83
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,519
Take him out and get ready.

84
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:26,720
Have him identify the body dumping site.

85
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:27,480
Yes, sir.

86
00:06:38,279 --> 00:06:39,079
Liar.

87
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:44,560
Did I just say the report was his?

88
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:45,680
Definitely not.

89
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,160
Oh, now I remember.

90
00:06:47,319 --> 00:06:48,759
This report seems to belong to Team Two.

91
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:50,079
I have to rush it over to them.

92
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,279
Sorry about that.

93
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:53,199
Let's go.

94
00:07:01,879 --> 00:07:04,000
Boss, you're amazing!

95
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,399
One-move takedown!

96
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:09,000
So, can I go out to the scene later?

97
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:14,439
You're not ready.

98
00:07:16,759 --> 00:07:18,360
How am I not ready?

99
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:20,279
Didn't I already do a task for you yesterday?

100
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:25,560
So petty. I only kicked you twice.

101
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,879
What did you just say?

102
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,879
I already apologized to you.

103
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,240
If you're still not satisfied,

104
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:40,160
how about this, punch me twice.

105
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:41,000
Kick me twice.

106
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,079
I promise I won't dodge.

107
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,000
Go ahead, kick me.

108
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,920
Think you're some kind of martial arts master?

109
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,879
Better than you, anyway.

110
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:49,959
Speak up.

111
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:54,680
Boss.

112
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:57,519
I joined the Major Crimes Unit to do great things.

113
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:59,639
You can't settle a personal vendetta.

114
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,000
How about this.

115
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,600
Let's have a real man-to-man fight.

116
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:04,959
If I win,

117
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:06,399
you let me go to the scene.

118
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:07,680
Deal?

119
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,199
Fine.

120
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:18,680
When I first joined the force,

121
00:08:18,879 --> 00:08:21,639
Captain Zhao beat me three times right here.

122
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:23,360
Only then did I get a shot at casework.

123
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,120
I'm different from you.

124
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:27,519
I'm a Kickboxing Champion.

125
00:08:27,879 --> 00:08:29,079
Titles won't win you this fight.

126
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,600
Boss, is dodging all you can do?

127
00:09:02,799 --> 00:09:05,000
To win, you need brains.

128
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,919
My skills aren't as good as yours,

129
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,200
but my strategy beats yours.

130
00:09:14,519 --> 00:09:15,279
Boss.

131
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,720
I picked the red gloves for you earlier.

132
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,600
Why aren't you wearing them?

133
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:21,279
Here, Boss.

134
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:25,600
Boss.

135
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:27,360
Don't you like the color red?

136
00:09:29,559 --> 00:09:30,120
Boss.

137
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:32,399
Red stands for passion and power.

138
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:33,960
Every strong fighter loves it.

139
00:09:45,679 --> 00:09:47,120
You don't like the red gloves...

140
00:09:47,919 --> 00:09:49,519
Are you afraid of winning, Boss?

141
00:10:15,399 --> 00:10:16,919
Boss, are you okay?

142
00:10:17,759 --> 00:10:18,919
I went too hard on you.

143
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,159
Let me take you to the hospital.

144
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:29,159
Boss, it was kind of an unfair win.

145
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,960
You were distracted by Red Gloves just now.

146
00:10:33,039 --> 00:10:34,240
The Red Gloves case has nothing to do with you.

147
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,240
Why quit being a patrol officer

148
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,399
just to become a detective?

149
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,720
Being a detective is my lifelong dream.

150
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,720
Detectives embody justice.

151
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:45,480
They're the nemesis of crime.

152
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,440
Their mission is to uphold justice,

153
00:10:47,519 --> 00:10:49,039
fight crime, and protect the people.

154
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,320
Are you writing a thesis?

155
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:54,519
Talking won't solve cases, you know.

156
00:10:56,399 --> 00:10:58,399
Sure, my basic skills right now

157
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,480
don't meet the standards of a detective,

158
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:02,639
but with all the talent I've got,

159
00:11:02,759 --> 00:11:04,440
being a patrol officer is such a waste of talent.

160
00:11:05,679 --> 00:11:06,480
Don't you think?

161
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,360
Yeah, it really is a waste of talent.

162
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,600
See? You agree, right?

163
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,240
Let me tell you,

164
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:14,519
being a patrol officer was so frustrating.

165
00:11:15,159 --> 00:11:16,960
Like a bird with broken wings,

166
00:11:17,159 --> 00:11:18,279
a dragon stranded on land,

167
00:11:18,399 --> 00:11:19,799
a steed that has stumbled,

168
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,440
an eagle with clipped talons.

169
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:25,200
Hey, Boss.

170
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:26,840
You'd better keep your word.

171
00:11:39,279 --> 00:11:40,080
Hurry up.

172
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:45,279
Let's go.

173
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:47,600
Captain Li.

174
00:11:48,039 --> 00:11:50,120
The body was found at Liuye Lake.

175
00:11:50,279 --> 00:11:51,679
This is Xinzhuang Ditch.

176
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,039
Is this the place?

177
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:02,919
Xiangxiang.

178
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:04,720
Don't kill me.

179
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,440
Everyone, listen up.

180
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:09,960
Go around from the side.

181
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:11,399
Don't contaminate the crime scene.

182
00:12:16,159 --> 00:12:16,759
Huh?

183
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:17,679
Captain Li.

184
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,200
Oh.

185
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:24,000
Captain Li is a forensic doctor wasted on detective work.

186
00:12:24,159 --> 00:12:25,080
Remember this from now on.

187
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,200
When you're at a scene with him,

188
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:28,080
medical gloves are a must.

189
00:12:36,399 --> 00:12:38,440
Boss, slow down, slow down.

190
00:12:52,519 --> 00:12:54,399
This really is the first body dumping site.

191
00:12:54,799 --> 00:12:56,159
What do you mean, first and second?

192
00:12:56,799 --> 00:12:57,600
What's going on here?

193
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:34,120
You're saying

194
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:38,559
Liu Xiang came back to life after Feng Bing dumped her?

195
00:13:39,519 --> 00:13:40,399
How do we prove that?

196
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:49,080
Boss, look at this bracelet.

197
00:13:49,519 --> 00:13:51,440
Wear gloves when handling any evidence.

198
00:13:52,039 --> 00:13:53,159
This is the last time.

199
00:13:55,279 --> 00:13:56,960
Feng Bing, recognize this?

200
00:14:00,919 --> 00:14:01,559
Yes.

201
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:04,120
It's Xiangxiang's. Yes.

202
00:14:04,399 --> 00:14:04,960
Take him away.

203
00:14:09,039 --> 00:14:10,000
Xiangxiang.

204
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:14,240
I think this is what happened.

205
00:14:15,639 --> 00:14:18,559
Liu Xiang realized Feng Bing wanted to kill her,

206
00:14:18,799 --> 00:14:19,879
so she opened the door and ran.

207
00:14:20,759 --> 00:14:22,600
Feng Bing chased her in the car and hit her.

208
00:14:22,879 --> 00:14:23,720
He saw she wasn't dead,

209
00:14:23,879 --> 00:14:24,799
so he strangled her.

210
00:14:24,799 --> 00:14:27,159
Then he dumped the body at Liuye Lake.

211
00:14:27,559 --> 00:14:30,399
But that still doesn't add up.

212
00:14:30,799 --> 00:14:32,639
Why was the body here in the first place?

213
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:33,519
Right.

214
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:35,360
Liuye Lake is so far away.

215
00:14:36,159 --> 00:14:38,759
Why go through all that trouble to dump it there?

216
00:14:39,279 --> 00:14:40,360
Look at these marks.

217
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,919
Steep slope, plus it had rained that day.

218
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,279
The dirt slope was too slippery.

219
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:47,440
Liu Xiang really struggled to climb up.

220
00:15:13,679 --> 00:15:16,399
If Liu Xiang, before being dumped in Xinzhuang Ditch,

221
00:15:16,399 --> 00:15:18,120
had really been hit by Feng Bing,

222
00:15:18,279 --> 00:15:19,200
with a slope like that,

223
00:15:19,639 --> 00:15:20,759
she couldn't have climbed out at all.

224
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,600
So there's only one explanation.

225
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:25,240
Before Feng Bing strangled Liu Xiang,

226
00:15:25,799 --> 00:15:26,799
he really didn't hit her.

227
00:15:27,799 --> 00:15:30,159
Liu Xiang was just choked into suspended animation.

228
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,120
After Feng Bing left,

229
00:15:31,399 --> 00:15:32,720
the rain would have woken her up.

230
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:34,320
That's easy to explain.

231
00:15:34,919 --> 00:15:36,360
After Feng Bing dumped the body,

232
00:15:36,799 --> 00:15:38,240
he got worried and came back to check.

233
00:15:38,679 --> 00:15:39,919
He happened to run into Liu Xiang,

234
00:15:40,639 --> 00:15:41,879
and ran her over with his car.

235
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,919
Then he dumped the body at Liuye Lake.

236
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:45,480
Hey.

237
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:46,799
Is the report out yet?

238
00:15:49,879 --> 00:15:50,440
Here it is.

239
00:15:52,799 --> 00:15:54,080
He really did hit a dog.

240
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:57,799
He hit a dog,

241
00:15:58,519 --> 00:15:59,720
but the person died.

242
00:16:02,039 --> 00:16:03,039
This is downright spooky.

243
00:16:03,039 --> 00:16:05,159
So the possibility of Feng Bing dumping the body at Liuye Lake

244
00:16:05,159 --> 00:16:06,159
doesn't hold up at all.

245
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:07,799
You're that sure?

246
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:10,480
Because last night I worked it out carefully.

247
00:16:14,039 --> 00:16:15,279
Liu Xiang got into Feng Bing's car

248
00:16:15,279 --> 00:16:17,120
at 5:45 in the afternoon.

249
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:19,639
Feng Bing drove onto the West Suburb National Highway,

250
00:16:19,799 --> 00:16:20,960
heading toward Longfeng Town.

251
00:16:21,679 --> 00:16:23,080
The two of them had an argument in the car.

252
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:23,799
Shut up!

253
00:16:25,200 --> 00:16:26,720
So Feng Bing drove the car really fast.

254
00:16:26,799 --> 00:16:27,919
It took 25 minutes.

255
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:30,399
Feng Bing drove to the edge of Xinzhuang Ditch.

256
00:16:31,159 --> 00:16:32,240
Their argument escalated.

257
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:35,159
Feng Bing strangled Liu Xiang and threw her into the ditch.

258
00:16:35,639 --> 00:16:37,440
Afterward, he quickly drove away from the scene,

259
00:16:37,639 --> 00:16:39,720
and got back onto the West Suburb National Highway.

260
00:16:40,759 --> 00:16:42,440
When he reached the road sign at Xinzhuang,

261
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:44,080
he hit a dog that suddenly ran out.

262
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:46,480
He hit the dog at 6:45.

263
00:16:46,799 --> 00:16:47,600
After hitting the dog,

264
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,559
he drove another 6 kilometers,

265
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:51,960
and dropped the car off at Youlin Auto Repair Shop.

266
00:16:52,399 --> 00:16:54,519
He dropped it off around 7:00.

267
00:16:54,639 --> 00:16:57,159
Your reasoning is really airtight,

268
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:59,919
but it can't be used as evidence for the case.

269
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,279
But it can connect the evidence

270
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,600
and point us in the right direction.

271
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:05,720
From the repair shop to Feng Bing's home in Longfeng Town

272
00:17:05,839 --> 00:17:06,720
is another 15 kilometers.

273
00:17:06,839 --> 00:17:08,279
That takes at least 20 minutes.

274
00:17:08,599 --> 00:17:10,119
And Feng Bing's neighbor can confirm

275
00:17:10,279 --> 00:17:11,599
that Feng Bing took a taxi home.

276
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:13,720
He got home at 7:40.

277
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:15,759
Let's suppose

278
00:17:16,319 --> 00:17:17,960
Feng Bing took Liu Xiang's body

279
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:20,640
straight from Xinzhuang Ditch to Liuye Lake.

280
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:22,039
That would take at least 40 minutes.

281
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:24,519
Driving from Liuye Lake to the repair shop

282
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:26,160
would take at least 45 minutes.

283
00:17:26,279 --> 00:17:28,960
There's no way he dropped off the car at 7:00,

284
00:17:29,519 --> 00:17:31,559
and no way he could've gotten back

285
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:33,079
to Longfeng Town by 7:40.

286
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:37,920
Boss, your reasoning is pure genius.

287
00:17:37,920 --> 00:17:38,960
You're in God mode, aren't you?

288
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,759
Captain Li hates it when people suck up to him.

289
00:17:42,359 --> 00:17:44,319
Do I look like the type who sucks up?

290
00:17:44,319 --> 00:17:45,400
I'm just speaking from the heart.

291
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:46,720
This is straight from the heart, I—

292
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:48,519
Enough, you're so annoying.

293
00:17:49,039 --> 00:17:49,920
The bottom line is,

294
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:53,519
how the hell did Liu Xiang's body end up at Liuye Lake?

295
00:17:55,559 --> 00:17:58,039
Based on Boss's brilliant reasoning just now,

296
00:17:58,440 --> 00:18:00,000
there's only one possibility.

297
00:18:03,039 --> 00:18:03,920
For sure—

298
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:06,240
there's a second killer.
